item.title: CVE-2023-41343|2023-11-03T04:11:29.131Z -- ragic -- no-code%20database%20builder
item.description: Rogic No-Code Database Builder's file uploading function has insufficient filtering for special characters. A remote attacker with regular user privilege can inject JavaScript to perform XSS (Stored Cross-Site Scripting) attack.
